     <div class="static-white-text-block terms">This privacy policy outlines how Matthew Vernon (‘us’, ‘we’, ‘Adddapt’) collects, holds, uses, discloses and otherwise manages your personal information and comply with our obligations under the Privacy Act 1988 (Cwlth). It applies to all of your dealings with http://adddapt.co and associated staff.
