       <br> How We Collect Your Personal Information
       <br>Adddapt collects your personal information for the following main purposes: – to keep customers (new &amp; existing) informed of new and existing products and services we offer; – to maintain contact with customers; – to notify customers, designers and the Adddapt community of events, products and services; – to manage and administer the products and services we offer; – to improve our websites to provide you with a personalised experience; and – to provide you with information about other products and services we offer that may be relevant to you.
