       <br>
       <br> We take reasonable care to ensure any personal information you provide us via our website is protected. For example, if we require your sensitive information our websites have electronic security systems in place, which include data encryption. Depending on your involvement with Adddapt and the type of information collected, user identifiers, passwords or other access codes may also be used to control access to your personal information.
       <br>
       <br> Use Of Cookies
       <br>You are not required to provide us with any personal information as a visitor to our website. You may choose to remain anonymous or to provide us with a pseudonym if you do not wish to reveal your identity. However, please be aware that if this is impractical we may be unable to provide you with proper services.
